frames.caption: A woman stands amidst a dramatic scene with a blazing wildfire in the background. Her expression is calm and composed, contrasting with the chaos around her. Birds are seen flying in the smoky sky, adding to the intense atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a mountainous area engulfed by a large wildfire. The woman stands in the foreground, seemingly unaffected by the surrounding flames and smoke. Birds are flying overhead, possibly escaping the fire.

frames.caption: A woman stands confidently against a scenic backdrop at sunset, with birds soaring in the sky. Her hair flows gently in the breeze, adding a dynamic element to the serene setting.
